      "Title": "Border Force officer"
    },
    "WorkRoute": {
      "Description": {
        "Html": "\u003Cp\u003EYou could join the Civil Service as a Border Force assistant officer, then apply for an officer post when vacancies become available.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETo do this, you\u0027ll usually need 5 GCSEs at grades 9 to 4 (A* to C), including English and maths, or equivalent qualifications.\u003C/p\u003E"
